{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1", "title": "Hiraeth's Wiki", "home_page_url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "feed_url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "My personal wiki or PKM", "icon": null, "authors": [{"name": "hiraeth"}], "language": "en", "items": [{"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "title": "About", "content_html": "<h1>My online wiki</h1>\n<p>The math note part, I'm using zotero, obsidian and mkdocs to create this wiki, and is hosted on github pages.</p>\n<p>&lt;!-- - [About](/wiki/About/in...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/", "title": "This is my Notes about computer", "content_html": "<h1>This is my Notes about computer</h1>\n<p>Concludes linux, software, latex, etc</p>\n<h2>linux and code</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/code/archinstall\">install arch</a></li>\n<li>[git note](wiki/code/g...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-21T11:54:01+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/3in1wiki/", "title": "\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u4e2a\u4ebawiki", "content_html": "<h1>\u4f7f\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u4e2a\u4eba\u5728\u7ebfwiki</h1>\n<p>\u5de5\u4f5c\u6d41\u662f\uff0c\u5728zotero\u4e2d\u9605\u8bfb\u548c\u6807\u8bb0\u3002\u7528zotero-better-notes\u63d2\u4ef6\u628a\u6807\u8bb0\u53d8\u6210\u6587\u672c\u683c\u5f0f\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230obsidian\u7684\u5e93\u6587\u4ef6\u4e2d\uff0c\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u7f16\u8f91\uff08\u6216\u8005\u7528nvim\u7f16\u8f91\uff09\u3002\u5728obsidian\u4e2d\u66f4\u65b9\u4fbf\u7b14\u8bb0\u94fe\u63a5\u8df3\u8f6c\uff0czotero\u53ea\u662f\u6587\u732e\u7ba1\u7406\u548c...</p>", "image": n